org.jcvi.jillion.internal.trace.chromat.scf.header

Class DefaultSCFHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jcvi.jillion.internal.trace.chromat.scf.header.DefaultSCFHeader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SCFHeader

    public class DefaultSCFHeader
extends Object
implements SCFHeader
    DefaultSCFHeader is an object representation of the header in a SCF File. The SCFHeader specifies the SCF version as well as offset and sizes of chromatogram data contained in the file.
    Author:
    dkatzel
